---
// Two-lane timeline showing Bill working in parallel with Kathy.
// Bill never pauses; Kathy churns in parallel; IRQ fires when she's done.
---

<figure class="coproc-timeline not-prose my-6 rounded-lg border border-ink-700 bg-ink-800 p-5 shadow-inner">
  <figcaption class="ct-caption">
    <span class="ct-tag">Timeline</span>
    Bill writes operands, fires the GO command, then keeps working
    on the main program. Kathy churns in parallel. When she's done,
    she raises IRQ; Bill briefly drops in, grabs the result, and
    keeps going.
  </figcaption>

  <div class="ct-stage">
    <div class="ct-lane ct-lane-bill">
      <span class="ct-lane-tag">Bill</span>
      <span class="ct-bar"></span>
      <span class="ct-marker ct-marker-start" data-marker="go" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="ct-arrow">↓</span>
      </span>
      <span class="ct-marker ct-marker-end" data-marker="rti" aria-hidden="true">
        <span class="ct-arrow">↑</span>
      </span>
    </div>

    <div class="ct-lane ct-lane-kathy">
      <span class="ct-lane-tag">Kathy</span>
      <span class="ct-bar ct-bar-kathy"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="ct-markers">
      <span class="ct-mark ct-mark-go">Bill writes operands → fires GO</span>
      <span class="ct-mark ct-mark-irq">Kathy raises IRQ → Bill grabs result</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</figure>

<style>
  .coproc-timeline .ct-caption {
    font-family: theme('fontFamily.sans');
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: theme('colors.ink.300');
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.65rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid theme('colors.ink.700');
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: theme('fontFamily.mono');
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: theme('colors.ink.400');
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .coproc-timeline .ct-stage {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto auto auto;
    gap: 0.65rem;
  }

  .coproc-timeline .ct-lane {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 4rem 1fr;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-lane-tag {
    font-family: theme('fontFamily.mono');
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    color: theme('colors.ink.400');
    text-align: right;
    padding-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-bar {
    height: 16px;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-lane-bill .ct-bar {
    background: linear-gradient(90deg,
      rgba(126, 231, 135, 0.4),
      rgba(86, 211, 100, 0.55));
    border: 1px solid rgba(126, 231, 135, 0.5);
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-bar-kathy {
    background:
      linear-gradient(90deg,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 18%,
        rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.45) 18%,
        rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.55) 80%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 80%,
        rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 100%);
    border: 1px dashed rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.4);
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-lane-kathy .ct-bar {
    /* (only the colored slice between 18% and 80% renders;
       border outlines the whole lane to suggest "Kathy exists",
       fill shows when she's working) */
  }

  /* Vertical drop arrows from Bill's lane to Kathy's lane (and back) */
  .coproc-timeline .ct-marker {
    position: absolute;
    top: -4px;
    bottom: -32px; /* extend below into Kathy's lane */
    width: 1px;
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-marker-start {
    /* anchored to "Bill fires GO" position */
    left: calc(4rem + 0.5rem + 18%);
    border-left: 1px dashed rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.55);
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-marker-end {
    /* anchored to "Kathy raises IRQ" position */
    left: calc(4rem + 0.5rem + 80%);
    border-left: 1px dashed rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.55);
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-arrow {
    position: absolute;
    left: -7px;
    bottom: -16px;
    font-family: theme('fontFamily.mono');
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.9);
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-marker-start .ct-arrow {
    color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.9);
  }

  .coproc-timeline .ct-markers {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 4rem 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-top: 0.4rem;
    position: relative;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-markers::before {
    content: '';
    grid-column: 1;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-mark {
    position: absolute;
    font-family: theme('fontFamily.mono');
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-mark-go {
    left: calc(4rem + 0.5rem + 18%);
    color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.95);
    top: 0;
  }
  .coproc-timeline .ct-mark-irq {
    left: calc(4rem + 0.5rem + 80%);
    color: theme('colors.rose.300');
    top: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .coproc-timeline .ct-mark {
      font-size: 0.55rem;
    }
  }
</style>
